1
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:36,300
[The names of characters, regions, agencies,
organizations, and other titles are fictitious.]

2
00:00:36,300 --> 00:00:38,600
[The scenes with child actors and animals
are compliant with the production guidelines.]

3
00:00:40,390 --> 00:00:43,200
[Episode 8]

4
00:00:52,270 --> 00:00:53,730
[In Tagalog] You idiots.

5
00:00:53,730 --> 00:00:56,100
Are you here just to play?

6
00:00:56,100 --> 00:01:00,900
Don't you have any plans
to earn some money for your family?

7
00:01:15,190 --> 00:01:17,500
You bastards!

8
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:19,940
Bring it on!

9
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:42,700
Get the dogs ready for the fight.

10
00:01:50,676 --> 00:01:54,350
- What is it?
- A website you set up in Korea was shut down.

11
00:01:54,350 --> 00:01:56,060
Shut down?

12
00:01:57,370 --> 00:01:59,740
This is the first work I created in Korea.

13
00:02:00,740 --> 00:02:02,770
Who was it again?

14
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:07,310
Right. That coach bastard.

15
00:02:12,300 --> 00:02:14,130
How...

16
00:02:20,690 --> 00:02:22,460
Right. Seong Wuk.

17
00:02:29,830 --> 00:02:33,070
Hey, Seong Wuk. It's been a while. It's Gwang Jin.

18
00:02:33,070 --> 00:02:37,530
This can't be. No one knows about this but us.

19
00:02:37,530 --> 00:02:40,770
Seong Wuk, you need to calm down.

20
00:02:40,770 --> 00:02:44,510
Hyung, I'm here right now. Let me check myself.

21
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:52,580
[Baek Seon Ja's resting place]

22
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:07,880
Here it is!

23
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:10,150
You scared me!

24
00:03:15,300 --> 00:03:19,930
Hyung, Min Ho was here! I found him.

25
00:03:19,930 --> 00:03:23,040
You took him out and checked yourself.

26
00:03:26,350 --> 00:03:28,790
Hyung, it's not that.

27
00:03:28,790 --> 00:03:30,930
Let's meet up soon.

28
00:03:38,210 --> 00:03:41,350
Get ready. Let's go to Korea briefly.

29
00:03:41,350 --> 00:03:42,710
Yes, sir.

30
00:04:24,070 --> 00:04:25,830
Cutting in line.

31
00:04:28,700 --> 00:04:31,130
Let's go to Jingwang University.

32
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:37,850
[17 years ago]

33
00:04:37,850 --> 00:04:40,350
Okay. I'll take the picture now.

34
00:04:42,860 --> 00:04:44,080
Should we say "Fighting"?

35
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:45,770
One, two, three.

36
00:04:45,770 --> 00:04:47,700
<i>Fighting!</i>

37
00:04:47,700 --> 00:04:50,050
[Volleyball equipment and uniform
sponsorship ceremony]

38
00:04:50,050 --> 00:04:51,780
All done.

39
00:04:51,780 --> 00:04:54,060
I'm nervous.

40
00:04:54,060 --> 00:04:55,930
Let's get going.

41
00:04:55,930 --> 00:04:57,410
We'll chew them up.

42
00:04:57,410 --> 00:04:58,940
Gosh, seriously.

43
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:02,130
- Good luck.
- We're in your care.

44
00:05:02,130 --> 00:05:03,660
<i>Fighting!</i>

45
00:05:06,410 --> 00:05:08,450
[2 years later]

46
00:05:13,810 --> 00:05:15,030
[Park Min Ho]

47
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:23,900
Min Ho, why don't you pick a pair?

48
00:05:23,900 --> 00:05:26,050
I'm okay. I'll just look around.

49
00:05:26,050 --> 00:05:28,720
I'm buying you a pair so you can
win the next game.

50
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,070
Okay? Pick a pair now.

51
00:05:30,070 --> 00:05:31,700
No, no. I'm really okay.

52
00:05:31,700 --> 00:05:33,600
Gosh, how stubborn.

53
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:36,520
Look at your shoes. Don't they smell?

54
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:39,190
Sunbaenim, we each picked a pair.

55
00:05:39,190 --> 00:05:43,020
They're quite expensive since
they're volleyball shoes.

56
00:05:43,020 --> 00:05:47,200
Don't call me Sunbaenim. Call me Hyung. Okay?

57
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:49,720
But not you. People will get the wrong idea.

58
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,230
Okay.

59
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:56,750
Hey, these are too expensive.

60
00:05:56,750 --> 00:05:58,100
I'll pick something else, then.

61
00:05:58,100 --> 00:06:00,320
- Which ones?
- Well...

62
00:06:01,220 --> 00:06:04,120
Give me a break. Buy three more of the same.

63
00:06:05,030 --> 00:06:06,160
For Min Ho, too.

64
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:08,160
No, no, no.

65
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:10,780
- I'm really okay.
- But I'm not.

66
00:06:10,780 --> 00:06:12,700
Hey, why...

67
00:06:12,700 --> 00:06:15,030
- Take him and find his size.
- No, no. I'm really okay.

68
00:06:15,030 --> 00:06:17,120
Okay, Gwang Jin. Follow me.

69
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:19,870
- Hold on.
- You're 280, right?

70
00:06:26,210 --> 00:06:28,480
I said I'm really okay.

71
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,820
They're too tight.

72
00:06:30,820 --> 00:06:32,340
You should get these, too.

73
00:06:32,340 --> 00:06:34,210
Let's get the matching ones.

74
00:06:44,580 --> 00:06:47,060
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

75
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:48,660
What are you doing?

76
00:06:48,660 --> 00:06:50,990
- Sorry, sorry.
- Do better, Seong Wuk!

77
00:06:50,990 --> 00:06:52,430
Fighting!

78
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:55,120
Let's score a point! Hey!

79
00:07:12,590 --> 00:07:15,050
Huh? I thought it was two serves.

80
00:07:15,050 --> 00:07:19,360
Geez. Gwang Jin will flip out
for not listening to him.

81
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:21,800
Couldn't he write more clearly?

82
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,820
You should've checked more carefully.

83
00:07:23,820 --> 00:07:26,340
- You read it, too.
- What are you guys doing?

84
00:07:27,350 --> 00:07:28,780
Hey, Min Ho.

85
00:07:28,780 --> 00:07:30,970
What's behind you?

86
00:07:30,970 --> 00:07:33,380
Did you receive a love letter or something?

87
00:07:33,380 --> 00:07:35,010
Give me.

88
00:07:37,420 --> 00:07:39,040
[Set 1 - Mess up on the full court serve... ]
[Set 2 - First serve out...]

89
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:41,230
Hey, hey. Don't embarrass me.

90
00:07:41,230 --> 00:07:43,790
We were just discussing a bit.

91
00:07:43,790 --> 00:07:47,900
He's right. We're reviewing our
mistakes from today's game.

92
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:52,210
You were reviewing?

93
00:07:53,330 --> 00:07:55,870
Didn't you do what was written here?

94
00:07:57,380 --> 00:07:59,080
M-Min Ho.

95
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:03,850
What happened to you guys?

96
00:08:11,620 --> 00:08:12,830
What do we do, Seong Wuk?

97
00:08:12,830 --> 00:08:15,120
What do you think?

98
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:32,180
What do I do?

99
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:41,540
Let's talk for a sec.

100
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:42,960
Get in.

101
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:59,780
Did you help your father with
what I gave you last time?

102
00:09:00,650 --> 00:09:03,570
Yes. Thank you for that.

103
00:09:03,570 --> 00:09:05,430
You don't have to thank me.

104
00:09:05,430 --> 00:09:07,400
Let me know if you need help.

105
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:11,340
Playing hard as you do now is your filial duty.

106
00:09:11,340 --> 00:09:15,130
You should go pro, make a lot of money,
and take care of your father.

107
00:09:15,130 --> 00:09:19,900
No one goes to a clock shop
these days. Don't you think?

108
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:25,940
To be honest, I was in a tricky
situation recently.

109
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:29,860
But Seong Wuk and Dong Hyeon helped me a lot.

110
00:09:29,860 --> 00:09:32,540
They're really good kids.

111
00:09:32,540 --> 00:09:36,200
I don't think I've asked you a favor.

112
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:39,650
Could you help me out, too?

113
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:43,900
You want me to rig games with your instructions?

114
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:46,400
No. I'm not telling you to lose.

115
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:49,740
Just do me a few favors, work hard again, and win.

116
00:09:49,740 --> 00:09:51,780
Nothing would change.

117
00:09:51,780 --> 00:09:53,390
I'll...

118
00:09:56,900 --> 00:09:59,600
help you out. Okay?

119
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:04,700
Until you join the V League. I mean,
until your career is over. Okay?

120
00:10:06,030 --> 00:10:08,810
I'll call the police.

121
00:10:08,810 --> 00:10:10,820
For rigging games.

122
00:10:12,220 --> 00:10:14,350
You can't do that.

123
00:10:15,580 --> 00:10:17,130
You already took a lot from me.

124
00:10:17,130 --> 00:10:19,550
I wouldn't have accepted it if I had
known it was for this.

125
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:20,910
Who would believe you?

126
00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:23,610
Everyone knows that we're close.

127
00:10:23,610 --> 00:10:26,230
I'm your official sponsor.

128
00:10:26,230 --> 00:10:28,380
Let's say you report me.

129
00:10:31,030 --> 00:10:33,040
You'll be an accomplice, then.

130
00:10:34,970 --> 00:10:37,120
I'll be punished alongside you, then.

131
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,620
Idiot.

132
00:10:38,620 --> 00:10:41,620
You watched too many TV shows, Min Ho.

133
00:10:41,620 --> 00:10:44,160
You want to be the protagonist?

134
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:48,540
You're saying you'll destroy your friends' lives.

135
00:10:48,540 --> 00:10:51,340
You're a scary bastard.

136
00:10:51,340 --> 00:10:53,650
I raised a tiger.

137
00:10:57,020 --> 00:11:01,790
Aren't you the one who's ruining our lives?

138
00:11:08,740 --> 00:11:10,780
I'll get off over there.

139
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:18,310
Min Ho, hold on.

140
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:22,140
I'm saying this so you don't get the wrong idea.

141
00:11:22,140 --> 00:11:24,540
I'm being sincere.

142
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:27,320
It's not easy to make money in volleyball.

143
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:31,100
This is the last chance I'm giving you.

144
00:11:31,100 --> 00:11:33,310
Think carefully.

145
00:11:33,310 --> 00:11:34,700
Okay?

146
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:37,430
I'll get going.

147
00:12:04,910 --> 00:12:07,900
<i>Son, have you eaten?</i>

148
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:10,140
Yes, I have.

149
00:12:10,140 --> 00:12:13,000
You don't sound so good.

150
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:15,600
Is something wrong?

151
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:21,550
I just saw someone doing
something very wrong, but...

152
00:12:21,550 --> 00:12:24,780
You're trying to ignore it,

153
00:12:24,780 --> 00:12:28,690
but it keeps bothering you.

154
00:12:28,690 --> 00:12:34,100
<i>Well, just do as you feel like.</i>

155
00:12:34,100 --> 00:12:37,660
<i>If that's how you feel, that must be the answer.</i>

156
00:12:37,660 --> 00:12:42,190
You know I'm always on your side, right?

157
00:12:44,410 --> 00:12:46,960
<i>Welcome.</i>

158
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:49,490
<i>Okay, son.</i>

159
00:12:49,490 --> 00:12:51,080
<i>See you later.</i>

160
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:53,980
Okay. Oh, Dad.

161
00:12:54,930 --> 00:12:56,530
Thank you.

162
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,950
Hey, Im Dong Hyeon.

163
00:13:08,970 --> 00:13:10,770
Where are you right now?

164
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:15,140
Dong Hyeon, listen to me.

165
00:13:15,140 --> 00:13:18,810
You'll get dragged around forever
if you don't correct things now.

166
00:13:20,910 --> 00:13:23,870
I'll report to the police today.

167
00:13:23,870 --> 00:13:27,750
That you and Jo Seong Wuk rigged games.

168
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:30,320
Why do you care?

169
00:13:31,430 --> 00:13:35,230
Dong Hyeon, turn yourself in now.

170
00:13:35,230 --> 00:13:38,400
If I do it, it's reporting. But if you do it,
you'll be turning yourself in.

171
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:41,940
I'm sure you'll get extenuated. Okay?

172
00:13:41,940 --> 00:13:43,230
Dong Hyeon.

173
00:13:43,230 --> 00:13:45,660
- Please.
- Geez.

174
00:13:49,180 --> 00:13:50,690
Sit.

175
00:13:53,900 --> 00:13:56,260
What are you doing, man? Come here.

176
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:15,530
I'm so disappointed with the decision you made.

177
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:24,670
You can't be like that.

178
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:42,730
Hey.

179
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:45,810
- You hit him, too.
- Pardon?

180
00:14:46,630 --> 00:14:51,220
If we let him be, he says he'll report
you guys to the police.

181
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:53,110
Will you just let him?

182
00:14:57,360 --> 00:15:00,860
- Give me.
- N-N-No.

183
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:11,330
Hey, hey.

184
00:15:15,450 --> 00:15:17,380
So what if you're the captain?

185
00:15:17,380 --> 00:15:19,550
Get lost, you bastard!

186
00:15:27,350 --> 00:15:30,330
H-He's acting weird.

187
00:15:33,490 --> 00:15:36,550
- Dong Hyeon, leave after five minutes.
- Okay.

188
00:15:36,550 --> 00:15:38,340
Seong Wuk, follow me.

189
00:16:15,690 --> 00:16:18,000
Aigoo, aigoo, aigoo.

190
00:16:23,710 --> 00:16:27,020
Yes. I found Min Ho.

191
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:31,090
Hey.

192
00:16:32,090 --> 00:16:33,810
Min Ho.

193
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:38,000
I-Is he dead?

194
00:16:39,490 --> 00:16:42,370
H-He's dead, right?

195
00:16:44,840 --> 00:16:46,560
What are you saying?

196
00:16:46,560 --> 00:16:49,940
He left the locker room earlier after a fight.

197
00:16:49,940 --> 00:16:51,440
Right?

198
00:16:52,510 --> 00:16:55,140
B-But still, Min Ho is-

199
00:16:55,140 --> 00:16:57,910
What? Will you call the police?

200
00:16:57,910 --> 00:16:59,820
You hit him.

201
00:17:01,540 --> 00:17:04,190
Dong Hyeon, Dong Hyeon, listen up.

202
00:17:04,190 --> 00:17:07,640
Min Ho left after having a fight with us. Okay?

203
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:08,970
If anything goes wrong,

204
00:17:08,970 --> 00:17:13,250
say you parted ways after
fighting in the locker room.

205
00:17:13,250 --> 00:17:14,870
Answer me, you bastard.

206
00:17:14,870 --> 00:17:18,710
Okay. Okay. Fine. Fine.

207
00:17:22,750 --> 00:17:26,670
I'll take care of your lives from now on.

208
00:17:28,530 --> 00:17:31,920
Dong Hyeon, don't worry so much.

209
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:34,620
I'll take care of everything.

210
00:17:34,620 --> 00:17:36,670
- Good work. Go home and rest.
- Okay.

211
00:17:36,670 --> 00:17:38,140
Don't worry.

212
00:17:40,060 --> 00:17:41,750
You stay.

213
00:18:17,890 --> 00:18:20,520
That's enough. Come out.

214
00:18:26,490 --> 00:18:28,180
Lift the legs.

215
00:18:28,180 --> 00:18:30,990
Bastard. Why are his eyes open?

216
00:18:32,310 --> 00:18:36,540
Lift him. One, two, three.

217
00:18:46,910 --> 00:18:51,410
Okay. One, two, three.

218
00:18:55,280 --> 00:18:58,550
My grandma died 10 years ago.

219
00:18:58,550 --> 00:19:01,350
She's finally giving me a great gift.

220
00:19:01,350 --> 00:19:03,080
I'm grateful.

221
00:19:03,080 --> 00:19:08,970
Hyung, we'll be okay, right?

222
00:19:10,540 --> 00:19:13,130
You bury dead people here.

223
00:19:13,130 --> 00:19:14,970
Right. Yes.

224
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:19,620
Grandma, you must be happy to have a friend.

225
00:19:22,250 --> 00:19:23,780
Let's bury him.

226
00:19:30,740 --> 00:19:32,540
What are you doing?

227
00:19:32,540 --> 00:19:34,500
Min Ho's uniform.

228
00:19:43,660 --> 00:19:47,540
Shit. Will you keep the shorts?

229
00:19:56,970 --> 00:20:00,040
Let's finish quickly and eat.

230
00:20:02,990 --> 00:20:04,140
<i>Here's the sentence.</i>

231
00:20:04,140 --> 00:20:07,870
The defendant Im Dong Hyeon will
be sentenced to five months in prison

232
00:20:07,870 --> 00:20:11,430
and 80 hours of community service.

233
00:20:12,650 --> 00:20:14,510
H-How...

234
00:20:14,510 --> 00:20:17,090
H-How is this fair?

235
00:20:17,090 --> 00:20:21,600
He gets five months in jail after killing someone?

236
00:20:21,600 --> 00:20:23,870
How could this be?

237
00:20:23,870 --> 00:20:28,730
My son's body hasn't even been found yet.

238
00:20:31,050 --> 00:20:33,970
Hey, hey, hey!

239
00:20:33,970 --> 00:20:37,090
Tell me where my son is.

240
00:20:37,090 --> 00:20:40,410
We should at least have a funeral.

241
00:20:40,410 --> 00:20:41,720
I didn't kill him.

242
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:44,020
Hey, tell me!

243
00:20:44,020 --> 00:20:46,070
Tell me, I said!

244
00:20:47,420 --> 00:20:49,660
I won't forgive you people.

245
00:20:50,980 --> 00:20:53,180
I'll kill you!

246
00:20:53,180 --> 00:20:54,540
You!

247
00:20:54,540 --> 00:20:57,420
H-How are you humans?

248
00:21:11,790 --> 00:21:13,730
This is what you're worth.

249
00:21:17,230 --> 00:21:18,710
You need to make more.

250
00:21:18,710 --> 00:21:21,780
Who knows how much we'll spend tomorrow?

251
00:21:21,780 --> 00:21:24,970
You need to make a lot, right?

252
00:21:24,970 --> 00:21:26,870
Hyung, by the way...

253
00:21:28,650 --> 00:21:32,550
Min Ho's father visited Dong Hyeon in prison

254
00:21:32,550 --> 00:21:35,100
and he seemed to know about everything.

255
00:21:35,100 --> 00:21:36,140
About what?

256
00:21:36,140 --> 00:21:37,690
About Min Ho.

257
00:21:37,690 --> 00:21:41,940
He said he knows Dong Hyeon didn't act alone.

258
00:21:44,150 --> 00:21:46,340
Bring me a truck later.

259
00:21:58,820 --> 00:22:00,850
Strike!

260
00:22:01,730 --> 00:22:03,510
Get off and check.

261
00:22:11,270 --> 00:22:13,600
Get it together.

262
00:22:13,600 --> 00:22:16,800
I said there are no CCTVs here.

263
00:22:29,900 --> 00:22:32,250
What are you doing?

264
00:22:32,250 --> 00:22:35,110
He's... I think he's dead.

265
00:22:44,330 --> 00:22:45,920
He's dead.

266
00:22:53,730 --> 00:22:56,330
Let's go and clean up his room.

267
00:23:22,280 --> 00:23:24,210
[Baek Seon Ja]

268
00:23:25,190 --> 00:23:28,010
Grandma must be bothered by the noises.

269
00:23:49,270 --> 00:23:50,820
Hey, it's me.

270
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:54,070
I'm in Korea.

271
00:23:54,070 --> 00:23:56,600
We should get together.

272
00:24:21,940 --> 00:24:24,680
