335
00:29:24,870 --> 00:29:26,370
Car accident?

336
00:29:26,370 --> 00:29:30,030
He had compound fractures throughout the body.

337
00:29:31,130 --> 00:29:34,810
The body will be moved to the
designated hospital morgue today.

338
00:29:34,810 --> 00:29:37,800
I'll contact them to arrange the transfer.

339
00:29:37,800 --> 00:29:40,470
Okay. Thank you.

340
00:29:46,250 --> 00:29:48,550
Car accident?

341
00:30:18,590 --> 00:30:20,260
This is it.

342
00:30:22,650 --> 00:30:25,380
All right...

343
00:30:30,900 --> 00:30:34,660
Long time no see, Min Ho.
[Body Bag: Park Min Ho]

344
00:30:34,660 --> 00:30:36,240
Take this.

345
00:30:44,820 --> 00:30:46,380
Jin Eon.

346
00:30:53,920 --> 00:30:55,920
Excuse me.

347
00:30:55,920 --> 00:30:59,090
There was an accident, apparently.

348
00:30:59,090 --> 00:31:00,640
Accident?

349
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:02,670
What are you talking about?

350
00:31:02,670 --> 00:31:05,100
Park Min Ho's body was taken?

351
00:31:05,100 --> 00:31:07,580
<i>We were waiting for it to arrive.</i>

352
00:31:07,580 --> 00:31:10,680
They caused a collision and took the body.

353
00:31:11,930 --> 00:31:14,990
Who would do such a thing?

354
00:31:19,250 --> 00:31:20,560
Excuse me.

355
00:31:20,560 --> 00:31:22,470
What's wrong, Go Eun?

356
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:30,150
- It's the gym Im Dong Hyeon owns.
<i>- There's been a fire at a gym in Seoul.</i>

357
00:31:30,150 --> 00:31:33,810
<i>The owner of the gym, Mr. Im,
was found dead at the scene.</i>

358
00:31:33,810 --> 00:31:35,710
Why would he all of a sudden?

359
00:31:35,710 --> 00:31:36,990
There's one more thing.

360
00:31:36,990 --> 00:31:38,880
<i>They're investigating the cause of the fire.</i>

361
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:41,810
<i>Based on player Jeong's confession,
Jingwang University's</i>

362
00:31:41,810 --> 00:31:43,890
<i>volleyball team coach, Jo,
who was being investigated</i>

363
00:31:43,890 --> 00:31:47,230
<i>for fixing games was found drowned to death.</i>

364
00:31:47,230 --> 00:31:48,900
<i>The police stated Coach Jo...</i>

365
00:31:48,900 --> 00:31:52,710
Im Dong Hyeon and Jo Seong Wuk
were definitely murdered.

366
00:31:52,710 --> 00:31:56,090
They couldn't have died
at the same time otherwise.

367
00:31:56,090 --> 00:31:59,300
Park Min Ho's body was stolen, too.

368
00:31:59,300 --> 00:32:01,550
All of these were done by the same person.

369
00:32:01,550 --> 00:32:05,510
A perpetrator who's never shown himself.

370
00:32:07,430 --> 00:32:09,410
Why would he...

371
00:32:10,990 --> 00:32:13,060
Mr. Park is in danger.

372
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:22,460
You didn't croak yet, old man.

373
00:32:23,460 --> 00:32:24,770
Who are you?

374
00:32:24,770 --> 00:32:26,220
Me?

375
00:32:27,520 --> 00:32:30,340
Park Min Ho.

376
00:32:32,730 --> 00:32:34,510
You aren't.

377
00:32:36,900 --> 00:32:39,000
Park Min Ho.

378
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:42,380
Jingwang University's volleyball player No. 10.

379
00:32:42,380 --> 00:32:44,020
Right side hitter.

380
00:32:45,520 --> 00:32:48,140
You totally lost it, old man.

381
00:32:48,140 --> 00:32:50,850
He likes vegetable bibimbap.

382
00:32:50,850 --> 00:32:54,730
There's no way he found Min Ho in this state.

383
00:32:58,680 --> 00:33:01,970
There must be someone helping you.

384
00:33:01,970 --> 00:33:05,550
Right? Who is it?

385
00:33:05,550 --> 00:33:07,760
He likes Girls' Generation.

386
00:33:07,760 --> 00:33:09,910
G-Girls' Generation?

387
00:33:14,430 --> 00:33:17,920
He likes to take photographs.

388
00:33:22,040 --> 00:33:26,060
You must be excited to go out, old man.

389
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,330
Dong Su!

390
00:33:33,330 --> 00:33:35,880
Who are you people? Move!

391
00:33:49,630 --> 00:33:51,020
Mr. Jang.

392
00:33:51,020 --> 00:33:52,590
So, it's you.

393
00:33:53,320 --> 00:33:56,560
The Girls' Generation member
who's been helping this old man.

394
00:34:04,020 --> 00:34:06,810
Are you the one who took Park Min Ho's body?

395
00:34:09,610 --> 00:34:11,120
Hyungnim!

396
00:34:24,160 --> 00:34:26,620
Mr. Park, are you okay?

397
00:34:29,370 --> 00:34:31,650
Wow. You're quick.

398
00:34:32,540 --> 00:34:34,320
Answer the phone.

399
00:34:44,750 --> 00:34:47,240
<i>That bastard was pretty strong.</i>

400
00:34:47,240 --> 00:34:50,250
<i>Yes. He must've been in the Special Forces.</i>

401
00:35:00,070 --> 00:35:03,770
Yes. Let's set up the equipment.

402
00:35:03,770 --> 00:35:05,960
Make it special.

403
00:35:11,330 --> 00:35:14,850
I smell a strong scent of cash.

404
00:35:35,250 --> 00:35:37,070
Cheon Gwang Jin.

405
00:35:37,070 --> 00:35:40,410
He's the grandson of Jingwang
Foundation's founding executive director.

406
00:35:40,410 --> 00:35:43,330
The money from the sports game
betting websites Im Dong Hyeon

407
00:35:43,330 --> 00:35:47,140
and Jo Seong Wuk used ultimately
went to Cheon Gwang Jin as well.

408
00:35:47,140 --> 00:35:48,500
Hold on.

409
00:35:48,500 --> 00:35:49,990
Founding executive director?

410
00:35:49,990 --> 00:35:52,510
The grave where Park Min Ho was buried.

411
00:35:52,510 --> 00:35:54,990
That was the foundation director's grave.

412
00:35:54,990 --> 00:35:56,730
Hold on.

413
00:35:56,730 --> 00:36:00,050
He hid someone else's body in his grandma's grave?

414
00:36:00,050 --> 00:36:03,140
- Geez.
- He's a total psycho.

415
00:36:03,140 --> 00:36:08,150
That's why Jo Seong Wuk was
Jingwang University's coach for a long time.

416
00:36:08,150 --> 00:36:10,930
The worst part right now is that

417
00:36:10,930 --> 00:36:13,430
