418
00:36:13,430 --> 00:36:16,630
But why did they steal his body?

419
00:36:16,630 --> 00:36:18,480
I just don't understand it.

420
00:36:18,480 --> 00:36:21,670
Because it's the only thing that's left.

421
00:36:23,130 --> 00:36:25,200
The ones who know the secret from 15 years ago.

422
00:36:25,200 --> 00:36:28,100
Im Dong Hyeon and Jo Seong Wuk are dead.

423
00:36:28,100 --> 00:36:30,190
And there's no evidence left anymore.

424
00:36:30,190 --> 00:36:33,100
Getting rid of Park Min Ho's body will

425
00:36:33,100 --> 00:36:35,940
forever remove the truth of that day.

426
00:36:35,940 --> 00:36:37,800
If so,

427
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:42,600
we won't be able to help Mr. Park, either.

428
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:50,520
That's why...

429
00:36:52,340 --> 00:36:54,920
we need to go immediately.

430
00:37:12,200 --> 00:37:16,490
I was a little worried that you
might want to go alone.

431
00:37:16,490 --> 00:37:21,150
Cheon Gwang Jin. He's feisty and dangerous.

432
00:37:21,150 --> 00:37:23,590
I might not be able to handle him alone.

433
00:37:23,590 --> 00:37:25,070
We have to go together.

434
00:37:25,070 --> 00:37:29,000
Of course. You can't handle that
crazy bastard on your own.

435
00:37:29,000 --> 00:37:32,240
Yes. We'll fight like crazy by your side.

436
00:37:32,240 --> 00:37:34,630
We don't have to go crazy, too, Hyungnim.

437
00:37:34,630 --> 00:37:36,110
Is that so?

438
00:37:43,610 --> 00:37:45,900
Hey, Girls' Generation.

439
00:37:45,900 --> 00:37:47,880
I never said that was my name.

440
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:51,020
How much did the senile old man pay you?

441
00:37:51,020 --> 00:37:53,690
I can pay you a lot more.

442
00:37:53,690 --> 00:37:55,830
I prefer not to discuss money over the phone.

443
00:37:55,830 --> 00:37:58,530
- Should we talk in person?
- Gosh.

444
00:37:58,530 --> 00:38:01,860
We're on the same page.

445
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:03,410
I'm glad we are.

446
00:38:03,410 --> 00:38:06,850
I'll send an address. Meet me in an hour.

447
00:38:07,830 --> 00:38:11,070
You won't find Min Ho's bones if you're late.

448
00:38:11,070 --> 00:38:14,450
Aigoo, aigoo. He's already fired up.

449
00:38:18,500 --> 00:38:20,790
[The Grandmother and Her Grandson]

450
00:38:29,790 --> 00:38:33,000
