459
00:40:30,940 --> 00:40:34,290
What do you think? Do you like this place?

460
00:40:36,910 --> 00:40:40,300
<i>You invited me. Shouldn't you
greet me in person?</i>

461
00:40:40,300 --> 00:40:42,100
Look to the right.

462
00:40:45,360 --> 00:40:47,430
<i>You see the door with Xs on it, right?</i>

463
00:40:47,430 --> 00:40:49,080
<i>Come in through there.</i>

464
00:41:04,940 --> 00:41:07,230
<i>What do you think?</i>

465
00:41:07,230 --> 00:41:09,710
